
# LUXURY WEDDING RSVP APP - COMPLETE UI DESIGN SPECIFICATION (iOS 18 INSPIRED, CORRECTED)

## OVERVIEW
This document defines the complete visual design system for the luxury wedding RSVP application, inspired by Apple iOS 18 glassmorphism and minimal modern aesthetics.

## COLOR PALETTE

### Primary Colors
- Background Light: #FFFFFF (Pure white)
- Background Dark: #121212 (Deep charcoal)
- Card Background Light: rgba(255,255,255,0.6) with backdrop-blur(12px)
- Card Background Dark: rgba(30,30,30,0.5) with backdrop-blur(10px)

### Text Colors
- Primary Text Light: #111111
- Primary Text Dark: #FDFDFD
- Secondary Text Light: #666666
- Secondary Text Dark: #AAAAAA
- Muted Text: same as secondary

### Accent Colors
- Purple: #5E239D used ONLY for:
  - Thin 3px left border on active sidebar item
  - Progress bar fills
  - Tiny input/button focus rings
- Gold: #BFA76F used ONLY for:
  - Logo text
  - Thin underline under section headings
- Success: #10B981
- Warning: #F59E0B
- Error: #EF4444

### Borders
- Light Mode Borders: rgba(0,0,0,0.06)
- Dark Mode Borders: rgba(255,255,255,0.08)

## TYPOGRAPHY

### Font Families
- Primary: 'Inter', sans-serif
- Decorative: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif for couple names, event titles

### Font Weights & Scale
- Light: 300, Regular: 400, Medium: 500, Semibold: 600, Bold: 700
- Hero Title: 3rem (48px), weight 300
- Page Title: 2.25rem (36px), weight 600
- Section Title: 1.5rem (24px), weight 600
- Subsection: 1.25rem (20px), weight 500
- Body Large: 1.125rem (18px), weight 400
- Body: 1rem (16px), weight 400
- Body Small: 0.875rem (14px), weight 400
- Caption: 0.75rem (12px), weight 500

### Special Typography
- Couple Names: Cormorant Garamond, 2rem, weight 400, gold color
- Event Titles: Cormorant Garamond, 1.5rem, weight 600

## SPACING SYSTEM
- xs: 0.25rem, sm: 0.5rem, md: 1rem, lg: 1.5rem, xl: 2rem, 2xl: 3rem, 3xl: 4rem
- Card Padding: 1.5rem (24px)
- Button Padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem
- Form Field Spacing: 1rem
- Section Spacing: 3rem

## SHADOWS & EFFECTS
- Consistent shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15) light, 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.3) dark
- Hover shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.2)
- No multi-layer shadows. Always soft and subtle.

## BORDER RADIUS
- Global: 0.75rem (12px) on all cards, panels, buttons
- Pills: 9999px (full)

## COMPONENT SPECIFICATIONS

### Cards
- Background: glass color (rgba + blur)
- Border: 1px solid theme border
- Shadow: as above
- Padding: 1.5rem
- Hover: scale(1.02), hover shadow

### Buttons
- Transparent glass look with subtle border
- On hover: scale + shadow
- On focus: purple ring (2px, offset 2px)

### Form Inputs
- Glass input, 3px purple left border on focus
- Soft focus ring

### Progress Bars
- Neutral track with purple fill only

### Status Pills
- Green/red/yellow glass, never purple/gold
- Rounded full with small padding

### Sidebar
- Glass background
- Active item has 3px left border in purple

### Tables
- Glass container, soft row hover rgba(0,0,0,0.01)

### Modals
- Glass container, shadow, radius 0.75rem, padding 2rem

## INTERACTIVE STATES
- Hover: scale(1.02), deeper shadow
- Focus: 2px purple ring, offset 2px
- Active: scale(0.98), slightly reduced shadow
- Disabled: opacity 0.5, cursor not-allowed

## RESPONSIVE
- Mobile: padding 16px, radius 8px, lighter blur
- Desktop: full spec

## ACCESSIBILITY
- Maintain 4.5:1 contrast for text
- Always visible focus indicators

## SPECIAL NOTES
- Theme toggle icon with transition
- Loading skeletons glass style with shimmer
- Errors use #EF4444 with transparent glass overlay

---

**This updated spec exactly matches our luxury iOS18 design while preserving your original structure.**  
No large purple or gold fills, pure backgrounds, consistent glass with blur + shadows, minimal accents, Inter + Cormorant.  
